high_descs: Turn left and exit the room on the left and walk down the passage to find the kitchen on the left and reach the countertop with the microwave.
Pick up the pot from the counter.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Cool the pot in the fridge and take it out.
Turn right to face the countertop.
Put the pot on the countertop to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled pot on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn left, go straight and left again to exit the room, then right and straight until seeing the countertop on the left, going left into it.
Pick up the pot next to the microwave.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Place the pot in the fridge and let it cool, then retrieve it.
Turn right and go to the countertop area.
Place the pot down on the countertop to the left of the sink drainboard.
anns.task_desc: Cool a pot in a fridge and place it on a kitchen countertop.

high_descs: Stand up turn around move towards the countertop.
Take the pot from the countertop.
Turn around move towards the fridge.
Keep the pot inside the fridge and take it back.
Turn around move towards the countertop.
Keep the pot on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Take the pot, keep it inside the fridge and keep it on the countertop.
